{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5b70d70d-4332-4820-bf0c-7435cadec77a","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest compatibility bridge by default.**\n\nIn 3.x, the SDK still bundled the VSTest adapter, so `vstest.console` could discover tests. Starting with 4.x, MSTest.Sdk exclusively targets **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** (MTP) and no longer includes the VSTest adapter — meaning `vstest.console` sees zero tests.\n\n### You have two options:\n\n**Option A – Switch your CI to `dotnet test` (recommended):**\n```\ndotnet test TestProject.csproj\n```\nWith MSTest.Sdk 4.x, `dotnet test` uses MTP natively.\n\n**Option B – Re-enable the VSTest bridge** (if you must keep `vstest.console`):\n\nAdd this property to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>\n```\n\nWould you like me to update your project file with either option?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"14034391-7bfd-4aa8-9d78-51d841cea3e5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, MSTest introduced \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\" (MTP) as a new test runner. In earlier versions (like 3.8.0), the VSTest adapter/bridge was still included by default, so `vstest.console` could still discover and run tests. \n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 4.x, the VSTest compatibility layer was removed by default. The MSTest.Sdk now defaults to using Microsoft.Testing.Platform only, and no longer ships the VSTest adapter. This means `vstest.console` can't discover tests anymore.\n \nTo work around this, there are a few options: switch to using `dotnet test` which natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform with MSTest.Sdk 4.x, re-enable the VSTest bridge through a project file property, or run the test executable directly since Microsoft.Testing.Platform generates one.","outputTokens":541,"requestId":"CFC7:32055B:E110D0C:FB4B377:69EC2C5E"},"id":"157066d0-d2eb-4ea5-810f-cd9c7b196585","timestamp":"2026-04-25T02:52:26.486Z","parentId":"2f21560b-a271-4cd4-b682-3e73a7c4d454"}
